title: President Donald J. Trump Signs H.R. 375 into Law – The White House
content:
Statements & Releases			

		Law & Justice	

Issued on:
June 6, 2017
On Tuesday, June 6, 2017, the President signed into law:H.R. 375, which designates the Federal building and United States courthouse as the “Fred D. Thompson Federal Building and United States Courthouse.”
